{"questionId":"9076659","questionHtml":"<p>A ball of mass <em>m </em>collides with a vertical wall with an initial horizontal speed <em>u </em>and rebounds with a&nbsp;horizontal speed <em>v</em>. The graph shows the variation of the speed of the ball with time.</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"https://ib-questionbank-attachments.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/tinymce_asset/asset/4819/Schermafbeelding_2018-08-13_om_18.26.37.png\" alt=\"M18/4/PHYSI/HPM/ENG/TZ2/07\"></p>\n<p>What is the magnitude of the mean net force on the ball during the collision?</p>\n<p>A. &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{m(u - v)}}{{({t_2} + {t_1})}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>m</mi>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo>\n      <mi>u</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mi>v</mi>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mn>1</mn>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>B. &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{m(u - v)}}{{({t_2} - {t_1})}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>m</mi>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo>\n      <mi>u</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mi>v</mi>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mn>1</mn>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>C. &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{m(u + v)}}{{({t_2} + {t_1})}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>m</mi>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo>\n      <mi>u</mi>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mi>v</mi>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mn>1</mn>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>D. &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{m(u + v)}}{{({t_2} - {t_1})}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>m</mi>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo>\n      <mi>u</mi>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mi>v</mi>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mn>1</mn>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>D</p>","meta":{"questionId":"9076659","referenceCode":"18M.1.HL.TZ2.7","subjectId":"46-dp-physics-last-assessment-2024","title":"A ball of mass m collides with a vertical wall with an initial horizontal speed u and rebounds with a horizontal speed v. The graph shows the variation of the speed of the ball wit","paper":"1","level":"HL","questionNumber":"7","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Core","Core","Topic 2: Mechanics","2.4 – Momentum and impulse","Core","Topic 2: Mechanics"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}